  "message": "test: add round 1 conformance and round 2 protocol negative performance baselines\n\nCaptures benchmark timing baselines for the conformance test suite:\n\n- round1_conformance_baseline.json: smoke_report_is_stable test mean\n  timing (~25.5s) for the full conformance smoke report\n- round2_protocol_negative_baseline.json: protocol fixture negative\n  test mean timing (~73ms) for protocol-level conformance checks\n\nThese baselines enable regression detection by comparing future runs\nagainst known-good timing envelopes.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
